articles.title: How To learn a new Skills to Keep Up With the century
articles.author: Hassan Alhalabi
articles.content: You may have owned an iPhone for years and regard yourself as an experienced user. At the same time, you keep removing unwanted characters one at a time while typing by pressing delete. However, one day you find out that a quick shake allows you to delete the whole message in one tap.
